ReadCaseAssignment1
data.value: select top(1) EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, SPD_ID, OFF_ID, OSP_CODE, OSP_DATE, CAS_NO from CKT_ASSIGN_CASE with(readuncommitted) where (@casNo = CAS_NO) and (EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @discontinueDate) order by EFFECTIVE_DATE desc

data.name: ReadCaseAssignment2
data.value: select top(1) EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, SPD_ID, OFF_ID, OSP_CODE, OSP_DATE, CAS_NO from CKT_ASSIGN_CASE with(readuncommitted) where (@casNo = CAS_NO) and (EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @discontinueDate) order by EFFECTIVE_DATE desc

data.name: ReadCaseRoleCase1
data.value: select T1.CAS_NUMBER, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.TYPE, T1.CASE_ROLE_ID, T1.START_DATE, T1.END_DATE, T1.EMANCIPATION_DT, T2.INTERSTATE_CASE_ID, T2.NO_JURISDICTION_CD from CKT_CASE T2 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_CASE_ROLE T1 with(readuncommitted) on (@cspNumber = T1.CSP_NUMBER) and (T2.NUMB = T1.CAS_NUMBER) and (T1.TYPE = 'CH') and (T1.START_DATE <= @startDate) and (T1.END_DATE >= @endDate)

data.name: ReadCaseRoleCase2
data.value: select T1.CAS_NUMBER, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.TYPE, T1.CASE_ROLE_ID, T1.START_DATE, T1.END_DATE, T1.EMANCIPATION_DT, T2.INTERSTATE_CASE_ID, T2.NO_JURISDICTION_CD from CKT_CASE T2 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_CASE_ROLE T1 with(readuncommitted) on (@cspNumber = T1.CSP_NUMBER) and (T2.NUMB = T1.CAS_NUMBER) and (T1.TYPE = 'CH') and (T1.START_DATE <= @startDate) and (T1.END_DATE >= @endDate)

data.name: ReadCseOrganization
data.value: select ORGANZTN_ID, TYPE_CODE from CKT_CSE_ORGANIZATN with(readuncommitted) where TYPE_CODE = 'J' order by ORGANZTN_ID

data.name: ReadCsePerson1
data.value: select top(1) NUMB, TYPE, OUT_OF_WEDLOCK, PAT_ESTAB_IND from CKT_CSE_PERSON where NUMB = @numb

data.name: ReadCsePerson2
data.value: select distinct T1.NUMB, T1.TYPE, T1.OUT_OF_WEDLOCK, T1.PAT_ESTAB_IND from CKT_CSE_PERSON T1 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_CASE_ROLE T2 with(readuncommitted) on (T1.PAT_ESTAB_IND = 'Y') and (T1.OUT_OF_WEDLOCK = 'Y') and (T1.NUMB = T2.CSP_NUMBER) and (T2.TYPE = 'CH') and (T2.START_DATE <= @startDate) and (T2.END_DATE >= @endDate) and (T1.NUMB > @numb) order by T1.NUMB

data.name: ReadGoodCause1
data.value: select top(1) CODE, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, CAS_NUMBER, CSP_NUMBER, CRO_TYPE, CRO_IDENTIFIER from CKT_GOOD_CAUSE where (@casNumber = CAS_NUMBER) and (@cspNumber = CSP_NUMBER) and (@croType = CRO_TYPE) and (@croIdentifier = CRO_IDENTIFIER) and (CODE = 'CO') and (CREATED_TIMESTAMP > @createdTimestamp1) and (CREATED_TIMESTAMP < @createdTimestamp2)

data.name: ReadGoodCause2
data.value: select top(1) CODE, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, CAS_NUMBER, CSP_NUMBER, CRO_TYPE, CRO_IDENTIFIER from CKT_GOOD_CAUSE where (@casNumber = CAS_NUMBER) and (@cspNumber = CSP_NUMBER) and (@croType = CRO_TYPE) and (@croIdentifier = CRO_IDENTIFIER) and (CODE = 'CO') and (CREATED_TIMESTAMP > @createdTimestamp1) and (CREATED_TIMESTAMP < @createdTimestamp2)

data.name: ReadGoodCauseCaseRole1
data.value: select T1.CODE, T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T1.CAS_NUMBER, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.CRO_TYPE, T1.CRO_IDENTIFIER, T2.START_DATE, T2.END_DATE from CKT_CASE_ROLE T2 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_GOOD_CAUSE T1 with(readuncommitted) on (T1.CODE = 'GC') and (T2.CAS_NUMBER = T1.CAS_NUMBER) and (T2.CSP_NUMBER = T1.CSP_NUMBER) and (T2.TYPE = T1.CRO_TYPE) and (T2.CASE_ROLE_ID = T1.CRO_IDENTIFIER) and (T2.TYPE = 'AR') and (@casNumber = T2.CAS_NUMBER) and (T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @effectiveDate) and (T2.START_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (T2.END_DATE >= @effectiveDate)

data.name: ReadGoodCauseCaseRole2
data.value: select T1.CODE, T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T1.CAS_NUMBER, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.CRO_TYPE, T1.CRO_IDENTIFIER, T2.START_DATE, T2.END_DATE from CKT_CASE_ROLE T2 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_GOOD_CAUSE T1 with(readuncommitted) on (T1.CODE = 'GC') and (T2.CAS_NUMBER = T1.CAS_NUMBER) and (T2.CSP_NUMBER = T1.CSP_NUMBER) and (T2.TYPE = T1.CRO_TYPE) and (T2.CASE_ROLE_ID = T1.CRO_IDENTIFIER) and (T2.TYPE = 'AR') and (@casNumber = T2.CAS_NUMBER) and (T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @effectiveDate) and (T2.START_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (T2.END_DATE >= @effectiveDate)

data.name: ReadOcse157Data

data.name: ReadOcse157Verification
